data.description: Beautiful and spacious well maintained brick bungalow freshly painted in the vibrant Chicago Chatham neighborhood! This 4 bedroom 3.5 bathroom home offers everything you need. Every inch of this home is finished offering the storage and space you want. The main level offers hardwood floors, a beautiful master bedroom complete with a master bathroom suite. The kitchen boasts granite counter-tops, subway tile backsplash, modern cabinetry and a complete premium stainless steel appliance package. Head upstairs and you'll find two large bedrooms with plenty of closet space and another modernized bath room with fresh new carpet.The fully-finished basement is perfect for entertaining with an inviting family room. Complete with another bedroom and finished laundry room. The walk-out basement leads to your two-car garage and backyard. This home is at a desirable price on a quiet street with easy access to public transportation, multiple expressways, Metra, restaurants and area conveniences. You will fall in love! Taxes show at $3,200 with homeowner exemption. Current taxes do not reflect exemptions.
